title: Careful: These Girls Are in Dangerous Nip Slip Territory
text:
Careful: These Girls Are in Dangerous Nip Slip Territory Jan 6, 2017 at 2:19 pm |   You're walking into the Danger Zone 
Call them what you will, but those round sacs of fatty tissue that women have displayed on their chests are like gifts to mankind, and the bigger they are, the more blessed you are. These particular ladies know what I’m talking about (whether they were naturally blessed or given a big blessing from their plastic surgeon) because they are goddesses when it comes to their top half. Feast your eyes and get your praise on! Advertisement Source: Instagram @pixiedustpt 
It’s not their fault; when you’re a woman with a massive rack, there’s little that you can do to contain those bad boys, and accidents tend to happen. It might be bad for them, but we love a good nip slip.
